text: Abdoulaye Diallo (born 15 January 1996) is a Senegalese football player who plays for Dinamo Brest on loan from Rukh Brest. ==Club career== He made his professional debut in the Segunda Liga for Desportivo Aves on 17 February 2016 in a game against S.L.
